<entry stylesheet="matteroverdrive:info/styles/guide.css">
    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">Tritanium Wrench</title>
        <preview index="0" size="2" style="float:left;margin-right:7px"></preview>
        <text class="matter-text text-block" style="width:190px">The $itemName can be used to dismantle most Matter Overdrive machines as well as machines from other mods. It can also be used to rotate all types of blocks.</text>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">To dismantle a machine instantly just right click the machine while sneaking and holding the wrench. Most machines will keep their configurations and items when placed after being dismantled.</text>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">To rotate a block simply right click it while holding the wrench.</text>
    </page>
</entry>
